[normal]The Task Force identified a number of actions that are needed in order to deliver these cost reductions
[normal]. The 
[normal]electricity 
[normal]market alone cannot deliver these cost reductions and a number of interventions are required by Government if 
[normal]a cost competitive CCS industry is 
[normal]to 
[normal]be 
[normal]delivered 
[normal]in 
[normal]the UK.   
